tps://www.thivien.net/Chu-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Nhu%E1%BA%ADn/Ngo%E1%BA%A1i-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-ph%E1%BB%A5/poem-bO87MSiR1zZnzGdxNOOchw">Ngoại trạch phụ - 外宅婦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Nhu%E1%BA%ADn/author-emAULa__NsnzXMwx2g06mQ">Chu Đức Nhuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%90%C4%A9nh-Chi/Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-t%E1%BB%89nh-li%C3%AAn-ph%C3%BA/poem-kmc4IXweJeTsqjRgFM3A6A">Ngọc tỉnh liên phú - 玉井蓮賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1c-%C4%90%C4%A9nh-Chi/author-7dFsTrXHz60sugbdOHPrjQ">Mạc Đĩnh Chi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Nh%E1%BB%AF-B%E1%BA%ADt/Quan-Chu-nh%E1%BA%A1c-ph%C3%BA/poem-t5SDq6ooOoPLPyHT8hFmCg">Quan Chu nhạc phú - 觀周樂賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Nh%E1%BB%AF-B%E1%BA%ADt/author-TDh6Z0N6kQIoYYwYA3fCGw">Nguyễn Nhữ Bật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Ng%C5%A9-Ph%C3%BAc/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Danh-Ti%C3%AAu/poem-sy3T3KlhUz6zNcOjDEuYIA">Tặng Trần Danh Tiêu - 贈陳名標</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Ng%C5%A9-Ph%C3%BAc/author-nDDIeBcr0ae9JEbukHfORA">Hoàng Ngũ Phúc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-V%E1%BB%8B/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-C%E1%BB%91c-bi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-N2zg6cPQ22Y_eMdJtcBX7w">Thượng Cốc biên từ kỳ 3 - 上谷邊詞其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-V%E1%BB%8B/author-cFaiJWajT_3vfsAWKg1raQ">Từ Vị</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
